      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI used in validation directly corresponds to the clinical decision QoI (absolute NIH); no surrogate substitution without documented justification.",
      "rationale": "Normalised index of haemolysis is both the regulatory decision QoI and the primary validation QoI. No surrogate quantities used. Wall shear stress validation provides supplementary mechanistic evidence. Full QoI alignment confirmed at MRL 5."
    },
    {
