      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same device geometry and within the clinical operating envelope; extrapolation distance documented.",
      "rationale": "All validation experiments performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry identical to the COU device. Operating conditions span the full clinical range. No geometric or operating-condition extrapolation required. Relevance rating 4 of 4 at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
