      "rationale": "All simulations converged to scaled residuals below 1e-6 for continuity and momentum; energy residual below 1e-7. Mass imbalance 0.003% at worst operating point. Iterative error contribution to NIH QoI estimated at less than 0.5% by Richardson extrapolation on iteration count."
