      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on benchmark studies for rotating hemodynamic flows. Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model used; model form uncertainty assessed by comparison with Taskin modified model — NIH predictions differ by 8.3%, within accepted model form uncertainty band of 15%. Sensitivity documented in report MF-2023-09."
